These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie, romance, adventure, martial-arts, crime, disaster
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching romance movies##2
5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | romance | martial-arts | documentary | adventure | zombie | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, teacher, designer, electrician, nurse, writer, social-worker
1. the writer is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the designer is on the right of the accountant##1
4. the designer is between the electrician and the accountant##2
5. the electrician is on the left of the teacher##1
6. the designer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Job   | writer | social-worker | accountant | designer | electrician | teacher | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
City: edinburgh, london, new-york, san-francisco, venice, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| City   | paris | berlin | venice | london | edinburgh | new-york | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, airplane, motorbike, subway, tram, bike
1. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the subway##2
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Transport   | tram | scooter | motorbike | bike | subway | jet-ski | airplane |

