.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, apricot, amber, pink, fuchsia, grey, ebony
1. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes fuchsia##2
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes pink is the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Color   | ebony | pink | grey | fuchsia | amber | apricot | aquamarine |

