.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-9::.
7 different games are played: canasta, whist, go, bridge, scrabble, poker, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |     3     |      4      |      5      |   6    |      7       |
| Game   | poker | whist | go | scrabble | backgammon | canasta | bridge |

