.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, february, december, january, july, march, june
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in january##2
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |   4    |   5    |      6       |     7     |
| Birthday   | march | may | december | june | july | january | february |

