.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-13::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, pony, guinea-pig, fish, frog, dog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |    6    |      7      |
| Pet   | hedgehog | fish | frog | snake | guinea-pig | pony | dog |

